Package: barktools
Type: Package
Title: Working with the Bark Scale
Version: 0.2.0
Author: Joey Stanley
Maintainer: Joey Stanley <joey_stanley@byu.edu>
Description: This package makes it easier to work with the
    Bark scale when analyzing and plotting acoustic data.
    One pair of functions convert between Hz and Barks and
    the other makes it easy to plot data in ggplot2 using 
    the Bark scale.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
URL: https://barktools.joeystanley.com, https://github.com/JoeyStanley/barktools/
RoxygenNote: 7.1.1
Depends: 
    R (>= 2.10)
